snippet.title: Wild Terra Online - Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Massively multiplayer online role-playing game with open world. Surviving in wild nature, harvesting, hunting, gathering, craft, unlimited building, pvp, sieges, treasure hunting, and even more!
Get early access: http://www.playwildterra.com/

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wildterraonline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayWildTerra
Developer: http://www.juvty.com/
